title: Games Of Thrones Season 3
description:
Welcome To my torrent!! Enjoy!!

Games Of Thrones S03E01-Valar Dohaeris
Jon is brought before Mance Rayder, the King Beyond the Wall, while the Night's Watch survivors retreat south. In King's Landing, Tyrion asks for his reward. Littlefinger offers Sansa a way out.


Aired March 31St, 2013

Games Of Thrones S03E02-Dark Wings Dark Words
Bran and company meet Jojen and Meera Reed. Arya, Gendry, and Hot Pie meet the Brotherhood. Jamie travels through the wilderness with Brienne. Sansa confesses her true feelings about Joffery to Margaery.

Aired April 7th, 2013

Games Of Thrones S03E03_Walk of Punishment
Robb and Catelyn arrive at Riverrun for Lord Hoster Tully's funeral. Tywin names Tyrion the new Master of Coin. Arya says goodbye to Hot Pie. The Night's Watch returns to Craster's. Brianne and Jamie are taken prisoner.

Aired April 14th, 2013


Games Of Thrones S03E04-And Now His Watch Is Ended
Jamie mopes over his lost hand. Cersei is growing uncomfortable with the Tyrells. The Night's Watch is growing impatient with Caster. Daenerys buys the Unsullied.

Aired April 21st, 2013

Games Of Thrones S03E05-Kissed by Fire
Robb's army is falling apart. Jamie reveals a story, to Brienne, that he has never told anyone. Jon breaks his vows. The Hound is granted his freedom. The Lannisters hatch a new plan.

Aired April 28th, 2013

Games Of Thrones S03E06-The Climb
Jon and the wildlings scale The Wall. The Brotherhood sells Gendry to Melisandre. Robb does what he can to win back the Freys. Tyrion tells Sansa about their engagement.

Aired May 5th, 2013

Games Of Thrones S03E07-The Bear nd the Maiden Fair
Jon and the wildlings travel south of The Wall. Talisa tells Robb that she's pregnant. Arya runs away from the Brotherhood. Daenerys arrives at Yunkai. Jamie leaves Brienne behind at Harrenhal.
Aired May 12th, 2013

Games Of Thrones S03E08-Second Sons
Daenerys tries to persuade the Second Sons to join her against Yunkai. Stannis releases Davos from the dungeons. Sam and Gilly are attacked by a White Walker. Sansa and Tyrion wed.

Aired May 19th, 2013

Games Of Thrones S03E09
Robb and Catelyn arrive at the Twins for the wedding. Jon is put to the test to see where his loyalties truly lie. Bran's group decides to split up. Daenerys plans an invasion of Yunkai.

Aired June 2nd, 2013

Games Of Thrones S03E10-Mhysa
Bran and company travel beyond The Wall. Sam returns to Castle Black. Jon says good bye to Ygritte. Jamie returns to King's Landing. The Night's Watch asks for help from Stannis.

Aired June 9th, 2013

About:
Seven noble families fight for control of the mythical land of Westeros
